lead_paragraph: A domestic violence complaint accusing Cleveland Browns quarterback Johnny Manziel of beating his ex-girlfriend has been referred to a grand jury, Dallas police said on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Dallas Police Refer Case Against NFL's Manziel to Grand Jury
